  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK793">
<l>kuṇaṉuṅ kuṭimaiyuṅ kuṟṟamuṅ kuṉṟā</l>
<l>viṉaṉu maṟintuyākka naṭpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Make friendship (with one) after ascertaining (his) character, birth, defects and the whole of one's relations.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
